Text Count - 0x00
---------
Text Count|x, shr 8 

The number of times Text opcode is called.
This is (x + 256*y).

e.g. Text Count|106, 2
Text opcode is called 618 times. (106 + 256*2)

Doesn't seem to be necessary ???

