Movie - 0x05
---------
Movie|ID, End State

ID
---
Which movie to play. (Document which movies are which !!!)


End State
---
0 - The movie ends on a black screen.
1 - The movie freezes on its last frame when it ends.

e.g. Movie|2, 1
Plays Usami appearing movie.

(Movie|${id shr 8}, ${id % 256}")
